data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET no fault of the seller. Only 7 years old!  Everyone loves this neighborhood, and now you can own a fantastic modern townhouse.  4 levels, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 half baths, and garage! Entering into the lower-level family room with a half bathroom.  The main level has beautiful hardwood floors, a half bathroom, and extra-large windows to see the beautiful scenery in the courtyard.  The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granted countertops, a huge island for entertaining, and a sliding glass door leading to the deck! The third level has a primary bedroom with a full bath and dual closets. There is so much more to this beautiful home. The fourth level is a loft-style bedroom with vaulted ceilings and another full bath. An open and bright space with room for an office! Don’t miss your opportunity to make it your home.
